          "children": [
            {
              "id": "fol267",
              "type": "text",
              "content": "Based on your utilization (148h/month, $96 effective rate), you're at 94% capacity. The market rate for senior product designers is $120–$140/hr. A 25% increase to $120/hr would generate an additional $3,552/month at current hours. I'd recommend starting with new clients only.",
